reviews.review_text:
Truckin Interesting to find Truckin as a first set closer. I found myself wondering where they were going to go with the jam which Jerry began in a full frontal attack. Ultimately Bob brings it back with an odd vocal refrain and more of a drop out rather than a snappy ending. Still, a great and unique version worth the listen.
Nice exploration in Playin
There are better China Dolls in 82.
